{"tid":1929363,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求神人搵一套動畫","createTime":"2020-03-17T01:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T01:59:43.000Z","uid":103645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b60175b8863968f5a4a3f7922c873432a1f1ee60","tid":1929363,"uid":103645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:39:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的,套動畫有一幕係喺古老火車(係金黑配色)穿梭時空個陣有敵人(定怪物?)襲擊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有一個西部牛仔大叔,佢隻右手係3連發格林機槍連接住個心臟,有特寫心跳聲,怦怦,怦怦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢條腰帶有唔顏色嘅子彈(寄存某種能量),入3種唔同嘅子彈,射出黎會有唔同形態的動物,例如有狼嘅外形<br />\nsorry,可能講到199<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔記得係咪劇場版定係TV版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肯定唔係銀河鐵路999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,個畫風好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跪求有神人可以搵到套動畫名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n動畫年代好似係2010年左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S97iOyc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS97iOyc.gif&h=c117c5dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5b23cbbc9875c079f0ee4a2